<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'About Mel', metaDesc: 'Meet Mel — the designer and developer behind Sites by Mel. Affordable websites built with care for small business owners.' }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav', { activePage: 'about' }) %>

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>About Me</h1>
  <p>Real websites from a real person who cares about your business.</p>
</div>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="about-placeholder">
          <span style="font-size:4rem;">👋</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="hero-badge" style="margin-bottom:16px;display:inline-block;">Hi, I'm Mel</span>
        <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:20px;">I build websites for people who have better things to do than build websites.</h2>
        <p style="color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.8;">Small business owners are busy. You're running jobs, serving customers, managing your team — the last thing you need is to spend weeks figuring out WordPress or paying thousands for a site you don't even own.</p>
        <p style="color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.8;">I build clean, fast, professional websites using plain HTML and CSS. No subscription bloat, no monthly platform fees, no mystery plugins. Just a site that works, that you own outright, that loads fast.</p>
        <p style="color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.8;">My templates are built around specific industries because a pressure washing company and a restaurant don't need the same things. Every template is purpose-built so it looks right from the start.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <a href="/templates" class="btn btn-navy">See My Templates</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>What I Believe About Web Design</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid" style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
        <h3>You Should Own Your Site</h3>
        <p>When I deliver a site, you get every file. No platform lock-in, no recurring fees just to keep the lights on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Fast Is a Feature</h3>
        <p>A slow site loses customers. Plain HTML loads in milliseconds. That matters for SEO and for real people on their phones.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Communication First</h3>
        <p>I respond fast and keep you in the loop. No ghosting, no mystery timelines. You'll always know where things stand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">💰</div>
        <h3>Fair Prices</h3>
        <p>A small business shouldn't have to spend $3,000 to get online. Good web design can be affordable — and it should be.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;max-width:580px;">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:16px;">Ready to work together?</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--gray);margin-bottom:32px;">Whether you need a quick template or a fully custom site, I'd love to help you get online and looking great.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/quote" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Send a Message</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

